	INSTALLATION

You need Apache webserver and MySQL database
mod_rewrite module enabled ofcourse in Apache

run the sql file 'db.sql' by one of these methods:

1. if you got shell access:
$ mysql -p < db.sql

2. using import method of phpMyAdmin:
upload 'db.sql' file and execute

Then, you need to edit config.inc file to setup database & base url

